  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Graphic Designer",
  "description": "<p>Are you a creative type? Not content to be a closet creative thinker, you love to dream of concepts and long to see them realized in brand campaigns and real life events and exhibitions. You have an interest in thinking of ways to make exhibitions more interactive, entertaining and fun. You have the Midas touch in graphic design and have a keen interest in digital media. Then this is the job for you.<br /></p><p><strong>About us</strong></p><p>C2 Global Exhibitions Pte Ltd is an exhibitions booth construction company with a strong global presence. Our team of talented and passionate individuals never fails to delight clients with winning creations, concepts and excellence in design and on-site operations.<br /></p><p>As a <strong>Graphic Designer</strong>, you will have the opportunity to:</p><p>1. Conceptualize event and exhibition branding using design software.</p><p>2. Create graphical adaptations of event or exhibition collaterals.</p><p>3. Work closely with 3D designers in realizing event concepts and design.</p><p>4. Work closely with account servicing personnel to fulfill clients’ requirements for designs.<br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p>1. At least 1-2 years’ experience in advertising or multimedia industry.</p><p>2. Possess at least a good Degree/Diploma in visual communications, digital media or equivalent.</p><p>3. Proficient in Adobe Illustrator, Photoshop, InDesign and Microsoft PowerPoint.</p><p>4. Plus point if you have knowledge of Adobe After Effects and Cinema4D or 3D Studio Max.</p><p>5. Strong graphic conceptualization ability.</p><p>6. Good design portfolio.</p><p>7. Willing to see a project through from conceptualization to FA production or online publication.</p><p>8. Willing to learn, responsible, good team player and self-motivated.</p><p>9. Only Singaporeans and PR need apply.<br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
